515static inline uint32_t am_hal_unstuff_bits(uint32_t *resp, uint32_t start, uint32_t size)
516{
517 const int __size = size;
518 const uint32_t __mask = (__size < 32 ? 1 << __size : 0) - 1;
519 const int __off = 3 - ((start) / 32);
520 const int __shft = (start)&31;
521 uint32_t __res;
522
523 __res = resp[__off] >> __shft;
524 if (__size + __shft > 32)
525 {
526 __res |= resp[__off - 1] << ((32 - __shft) % 32);
527 }
528 return __res &__mask;
529}
530
531static inline uint32_t am_hal_unstuff_bytes(uint32_t *ext_csd, uint32_t start, uint32_t size)
532{
533 int i;
534 const uint32_t __size = size;
535 uint32_t __res = 0x0;
536 const uint8_t *__p = (const uint8_t *)ext_csd;
537 for (i = 0; i < __size; i++)
538 {
539 __res |= __p[start + i] << 8 * i;
540 }
541 return __res;
542}
